∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime] (hodd : p ≠ 2), 
  ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p →
    let F (n : ℕ) := (Finset.range (p - 1)).sum (λ k, (k + 1) * n ^ k) in
    F a ≢ F b [ZMOD p]
∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact (Nat.Prime p)], p ≠ 2 → ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p → let F (n : ℕ) := ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n ^ i in F a ≠ F b [MOD p]

∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact (Nat.Prime p)], p > 2 →
  ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p → a ≠ b →
  (∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * a ^ i) % p ≠ (∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * b ^ i) % p

∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime] (hodd : p % 2 = 1), 
  ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p → 
    (let F (n : ℕ) := Finset.sum (Finset.range (p - 1)) (λ k, (k + 1) * n ^ k) in 
      ¬(F a ≡ F b [MOD p]))
∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime], p ≠ 2 → ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p → a ≠ b → F a % p ≠ F b % p

∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime] (h : p > 2),
  ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p →
  let F := λ n, (Finset.range (p - 1)).sum (λ k, (k + 1) * n ^ k)
  in F a % p ≠ F b % p

∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime] (h_odd : p % 2 = 1) {a b : ℤ}, a ≠ b → a ∈ Finset.range p → b ∈ Finset.range p → (let F n := Finset.sum (Finset.range (p - 1)) (λ k, (k + 1) * n ^ k) in F a ≢ F b [ZMOD ↑p])

∀ (p : ℕ) [inst : Fact (p.Prime ∧ p > 2)],
  ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p → 
  let F (n : ℕ) := ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n ^ i 
  in F a % p ≠ F b % p

∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime], p ≠ 2 →
  ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p →
  let F (n : ℕ) := ∑ i in Finset.range (p - 1), (i + 1) * n ^ i 
  in (F a) % p ≠ (F b) % p

∀ {p : ℕ} [hp : Fact p.Prime], p > 2 →
  ∀ {a b : ℕ}, a ≠ b → a < p → b < p →
  let F := λ n, (Finset.range (p - 1)).sum (λ k, (k + 1) * n ^ k) in
  F a % p ≠ F b % p
